name: Hash Hunter
description:
NLP to transaction private AI agent. Support cross chain transfers, swaps and p2p transfers on 12+ EVM chains and SVM.  We enable users and autonomous agents to access resources and execute transactions seamlessly across different ecosystems.

Example interactions:

Bridge all of my SOL to ETH
Move all of my OP to ETH
Buy 0x....... on ETH with 1 ETH

We support also sequenced actions

Bridge all of my SOL to ETH and buy 0x.... on BNB

Bridge all of my ETH to SOL and buy .....pump

Check our docs for more details on  - docs.hashhunter.ai


We have Non-custodial wallet management app and TG Bot

https://hashhunter.app
https://t.me/TheHashHunterBot
https://x.com/hashhunterbot
https://hashhunter.ai

Developed by HEAA Protocol
Website: heaa.xyz
X: https://x.com/HEAAProtocol


Deployed on Phala TEE Attestation:(https://proof.t16z.com/reports/9d4d27c68b878a441670ad49df5d750f5930de2953a947ce6548e46dde18ef65)
